{"tid":2223314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點識到酒量好的女仔？","createTime":"2020-09-29T17:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T11:54:48.000Z","uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9410583b886f6cea7d5513138b738c994e5a59c","tid":2223314,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"以前 Ex 都有啲鍾意蒲同劈酒，可能可以劈到半支威士忌，十個 shot 到。點知而家出返嚟識人，好多人都唔飲酒或者飲少少就醉同嘔。<br />\n<br />\n我酒量都係差唔多，有時做嘢要應酬都可以飲頗多。覺得女人酒量好幾緊要，首先唔會太易醉保護到自己，第二飲吓酒心情都會舒舒啲。<br />\n<br />\n唔好建議我識酒吧拳手/夜總會小姐。"},{"pid":"e0d4b77a6e385efd1cee8298c6e459892219cf0d","tid":2223314,"uid":44854,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"要女人陪你去應酬真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5d4e0d54515798ca25834a62cf0497bb33c934","tid":2223314,"uid":136900,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"個ex中意蒲同劈都仲敢搵中意飲酒嘅女仔"},{"pid":"4ed15e4a9c15feb863e93c03d89145fcda44de10","tid":2223314,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0d4b77a6e385efd1cee8298c6e459892219cf0d","tid":2223314,"uid":44854,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"要女人陪你去應酬真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"唔係要陪應酬，只係平時想私下飲。"},{"pid":"2d881a30c28f16468d74a75dd896a0ff659c4cf9","tid":2223314,"uid":364806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7496e35badcb6873fc0061704a886b3321713127","tid":2223314,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦收皮啦收皮啦"},{"pid":"fc42257579aed32b215870d404d4434035c757a7","tid":2223314,"uid":363503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"[恒大樹大][開學須知]請小心狗二代羅超賢同陳懷謙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2220151\" data-auto-lin